post0.title: Test
post0.content: Auto-convert markdown files To Posts . fastpages will automatically convert markdown files saved into this directory as blog posts! . You must save your notebook with the naming convention YYYY-MM-DD-*.md. Examples of valid filenames are: . 2020-01-28-My-First-Post.md 2012-09-12-how-to-write-a-blog.md . Resources . Jekyll posts | Example markdown post | .
